{
  "stem": "10699.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was all in my imagination.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It had all-- I had outgrown it all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's all I could say about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even where I was born in Metz, we lived there till I was eight years old.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went back, and I only remember that it was a house with a very big entrance.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to my surprise, when I went back, the entrance had shrunk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The house had shrunk, and everything had shrunk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's-- where you see it as a child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In '39, we moved with our car.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We took a few things this time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because my mother was always afraid of a war, because she went through the 14-18 War.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was always afraid, and she was terribly afraid already in '38.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she-- we followed the news, you know, coming out of Germany from early on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From '33, we followed it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother was very, very concerned and very worried.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in '39, when we did go into the interior to Blamont, which was about 200 kilometers or miles from Sarreguemines.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had rented a little home, an apartment, where an old lady and her daughter kept it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had that house, and we had one floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were now refugees.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And instead of continuing with studies-- everything had stopped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- my parents found a job for me in an office, and my brothers studied from home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They studied from home, correspondence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I found a job at a company whose-- the first job they gave me was bookkeeping, because I had studied also commercial at the school.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They gave me bookkeeping, and I was very bored, so they gave me another job with a director who had polio.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was very kind, and he could see that I was very shy with the telephone and very shy with doing certain things.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he encouraged me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For six months, I worked for him, until we had to run again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and my brothers just studied.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we just lived there as well as we could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But you mustn't forget that as soon as the war broke out, the Germans didn't need to go to fight the Ligne Maginot.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They went around it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Therefore, the [NON-ENGLISH] was very soon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived in that apartment, and we saw the soldiers, in the winter of 1940, coming down with horse and cart, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a terrible sight, thinking that the Germans-- you know, with their strong army, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our French Army was absolutely not ready for such a war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we stayed there in Blamont and watched the events till June 1940.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You managed to live some kind of life there?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was full of people from our town, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some French Army personnel in the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in those days, you still found food, and you could still live more or less and find a way to get on with life.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] That's right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father tried to-- he had public reports on merchandise, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he tried to sell some of it so that money was coming in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so all what we had to do is really, we could only eat and wait for the events, thinking that maybe we'd soon-- life would go back to normal.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But of course it didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in-- in-- we just lived through the winter there and followed the events.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by June 1940, of course, the whole-- the Germans invaded France.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we were on the running.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a car, but of course, there was no petrol.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The car wouldn't go anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had to-- from that company where I was working, they were willing to put us, a whole lot of people, into one of their vans.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were on the road like everybody else, with millions of others, some in cars, some on bikes, some with prams with their goods in it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody was on the march.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you mustn't forget that the Italians were also our enemies, and therefore, they were bombarding us on the way down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we-- we were running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were-- from the beginning of June, we were running down, and the Germans were following us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were behind us, the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we reached-- by the time we reached-- that was [NON-ENGLISH], the Germans had caught up with us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were behind us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were being bombarded.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
